fisrt run "Xorg &"

use help for information
example:mplayer --help
		mplayer -vo help
		mplayer -ao for audio help


hardware decode:
mplayer "video_name" -vo vaapi -ao alsa

soft decode:
mplayer "video_name" -ao alsa
but the soft decode is slower than the hardware decode

"-ao alsa" is for mplayer use the ALSE to play the voice

then you can see a movie,enjoy yourself!
